I know we fixed the original problem that was causing a crash and tested it, so I'm guessing that something more is coming into play here... possibly the use of `..\..` in your project. (BTW, did you use the project editor or create it by hand?)

This may be a separate bug but for now can you provide us with a (sanitized) copy of your nunit project to serve as a repro?
